Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:50.55,Main,,0,0,0,,We hated you from the beginning--\Nand loved you from the beginning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:56.60,Main,,0,0,0,,And so we wanted to become true\Nfriends with you. To cross the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:02.27,Main,,0,0,0,,A bear has crossed the Wall of Severance,\Nour only line of defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.27,0:01:05.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika Izumino has lost her life to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:11.49,Main,,0,0,0,,and we are now unable to reach\NKatyusha Akae, Konomi Yurikawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:15.20,Main,,0,0,0,,and several other students.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:22.42,MainTop,,0,0,0,,We are facing our greatest crisis\Nsince the Day of Severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:27.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Happily, the bear we believe to have\Nbeen the invader was shot last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:30.13,Main,,0,0,0,,but we mustn't let our guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:36.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Understand that the friends sitting next\Nto you are the keys to your protection now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:39.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Never be alone for a moment,\Neven on school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:43.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You must protect each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:47.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be the one to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:57.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:58.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.33,0:02:01.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Why? I mean, yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:05.25,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not what I intended...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:10.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine then, Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:11.05,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Mitsuko Yurizono・(Yuri)"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.05,0:02:18.60,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Damn, you're rejecting me? Well, fine.\NThat's what I like about you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:22.06,Main,,0,0,0,,The fun's only beginning, Kureha Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:26.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a {\i1}good {\i0}working over,\Nand then I'll eat you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:33.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikumaaaaaaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:34.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:41.58,Main,,0,0,0,,"INVISIBLE STORM"\N{\i1}Viens avec moi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Church chimes echo in the distance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:47.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Offer up a prayer and betray today{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:53.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wander in a dark forest, then become{\i0}\N{\i1}the morning moon at the Wall of Severance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:55.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't join the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:59.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once I've made you stickier{\i0}\N{\i1}with sweet, thin honey{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:04.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, approve me, I'll be a good girl{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:09.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Picture-book pages dancing on{\i0}\N{\i1}the breeze shake up shadowy memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.61,0:03:15.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:21.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be waiting you-know-where,{\i0}\N{\i1}in an empty world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:26.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if everything falls apart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:33.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you have to gracefully writhe,{\i0}\N{\i1}even if you have to bend space-time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:37.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Find me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:48.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flower petals will slowly{\i0}\N{\i1}enfold us on a starry night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:50.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:52.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:55.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:04.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}J'ai besoin de toi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:10.79,MainTop,,0,0,0,,How are you? Have you calmed down a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:12.00,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:12.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:14.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:15.92,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a bad liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:19.97,Main,,0,0,0,,You're just like Reia that way--earnest to a fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:22.43,Main,,0,0,0,,"Reia"... my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:23.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:29.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You really remind me of her.\NYou're so much like your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:37.07,Main,,0,0,0,,You mustn't suffer in silence, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:42.49,Main,,0,0,0,,The pain of losing a loved one grows\Nworse the more you try to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:44.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I know that all too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I lost Reia--your mother--that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:58.63,Main,,0,0,0,,She was my dear friend,\Nand I'll never have another like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:01.43,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I was so happy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:07.56,Main,,0,0,0,,when you came to this school\Nand brought that flowerbed back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:13.52,Main,,0,0,0,,That place held special\Nmemories for Reia and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:15.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:21.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, so do I. They stole the ones we loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:22.78,Main,,0,0,0,,There's another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:23.99,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.99,Main,,0,0,0,,There's one more bear here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:31.50,Main,,0,0,0,,But surely Yurizono exterminated\Nthe bear that attacked Izumino...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:35.08,Main,,0,0,0,,She didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:38.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I saw them! There's one more bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:43.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm positive it's still in this school somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:52.52,Main,,0,0,0,,"School" really is an excellent system.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:58.27,Main,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is stay here\Nand wait for the time to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:00.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurizono!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:05.87,MainTop,,0,0,0,,I'm volunteering to fill in\Nfor Yurikawa as chair today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:11.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Well done, Oniyama! Class friendship\Nstarts with individual responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:15.29,Main,,0,0,0,,The leadership you're showing is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:24.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Strong people are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:27.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yurizono...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:29.76,Main,,0,0,0,,You can call me Mitsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:32.56,Main,,0,0,0,,The lily opens!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:40.90,Main,,0,0,0,,There's my good girl.\NNow, hurry and let me eat Kureha Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:47.78,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Lulu Yurigasaki・(Yuri)"    "Ginko Yurishiro・(Yuri)"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:49.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:55.67,Main,,0,0,0,,There's one more bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:05.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive bears. I'll ruin bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:11.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl-brrrr...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:15.27,Main,,0,0,0,,She's totally itching to shoot a bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:20.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, and we came here to beat\Nthat icky Mitsuko Yurizono to it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:24.78,Main,,0,0,0,,But we can't approach her in that mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:31.03,Main,,0,0,0,,But who knew there'd be a rival bear\Nat that school who saw through us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:34.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicious smell. Growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:38.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Geez, Ginko, you're not even listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:42.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki must be a really tasty girl, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:47.55,Main,,0,0,0,,In answer to Pope Urban II's call,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:53.89,Main,,0,0,0,,the armies of kings and nobles\Nacross Western Europe gathered
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:57.60,Main,,0,0,0,,to form the first army of crusaders in 1096...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:02.56,Main,,0,0,0,,And thus began a long series of wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.86,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:08.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, Miss Forgetful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:32.72,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, girls, the test will...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:34.51,Main,,0,0,0,,...not include this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:37.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You better believe it'll include this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:48.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika... Time moves so slowly\Nwhen you're not in class with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:54.16,Main,,0,0,0,,What this means is that the Crusades\Nexposed the people of Western Europe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:09:00.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Will I start to forget everything now?\NForget that day, that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:06.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Will I eventually forget love\Nand be invisible like the others...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Your mother's flowerbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:20.10,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:25.44,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Mom told me that back\Nwhen she was a student here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:28.40,Main,,0,0,0,,she built it with her special friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:31.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, so that's why you love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:36.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I want to make it full of flowers again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:39.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. You didn't give up, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:46.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Your mother's precious garden...\NSo that's your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,My love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:50.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:57.64,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I won't give up either, Kureha.\NNot on my precious love...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:10:01.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't forget. I'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:05.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't give up on love either, Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:10.74,Main,,0,0,0,,We must be invisible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:12.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Let us begin the Exclusion Ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:13.53,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Exclusion Ceremony・(Exclusion)"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:16.95,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Friends" are more important\Nthan anything else, agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:21.33,Main,,0,0,0,,The friends here in this\Nclassroom right now: that's {\i1}us{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:25.21,Main,,0,0,0,,People who contradict our\Nfeelings are a disgrace, agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:28.04,Main,,0,0,0,,People who stick out from our crowd\Nare just no good, agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:31.26,Main,,0,0,0,,People who refuse to fit in\Nwith us are a nuisance, agreed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:34.05,Main,,0,0,0,,People like that who can't follow social cues...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:35.38,Main,,0,0,0,,...are evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:36.76,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Can't Follow Social Cues = Evil・(Exclusion)"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:41.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika Izumino got killed\Nby a bear because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:46.35,Main,,0,0,0,,It's only natural, isn't it? Because she was evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:50.65,Main,,0,0,0,,We must decide who the next evil to exclude is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:53.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's search evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:10:59.74,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"The Invisible Storm・(Exclusion)"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.02,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"5. Hinako Serina"\N"6. Uchiko Ai"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:28.19,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"4. Saori Shimabukuro"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:29.36,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"3. Aoi Uezu"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:31.65,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"2. Karen Tanaka"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:32.78,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"1. Evil = Kureha Tsubaki"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:35.24,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Evil = Kureha Tsubaki"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:38.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Select! The time has finally come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:43.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to eat her--Kureha Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Slurp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:49.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Grrrrrr...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:05.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, did you have fun\Nwith your friend again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:11.56,Main,,0,0,0,,That's great! You really\Nlove her, don't you, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:18.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You know what? As long as you don't\Nforget love, you'll never be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:23.99,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. If I don't forget love,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:25.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:27.83,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:36.38,Main,,0,0,0,,A storm and flood warning has just\Nbeen issued for the greater metro area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.22,Main,,0,0,0,,We're seeing violent rain and wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:41.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Residents in some areas\Nhave been advised to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.89,Main,,0,0,0,,If this applies to you,\Nevacuate immediately in accordance
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:46.85,Main,,0,0,0,,--with your township's instr--\N--Oh no--the flowerbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:57.78,Main,,0,0,0,,"Bear Warning"\N"Storm and Flood Warning"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:16.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:28.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Aren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:31.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:37.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sumika.\NThank you for staying my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:43.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure. Thanks for staying mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:51.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't back down on my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:14:00.42,Main,,0,0,0,,To live means to constantly forget,\Nback down, and cast away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:08.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Those who cannot replace the old\Nwith the new will eventually perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:13.02,Main,,0,0,0,,We beasts never live in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:17.48,Main,,0,0,0,,All that exists is the present,\Nthe emotions we feel right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:22.49,Main,,0,0,0,,The mood, the rhythm of\Nthis moment is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:29.91,Main,,0,0,0,,The invisible ones decide\Nhow to run closed worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:34.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Grrrrrrr.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:40.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, Ginko,\NI'll never forget the day I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:45.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You found my love. You brought it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:51.06,Main,,0,0,0,,So no matter what happens,\NI won't give up on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:54.06,Main,,0,0,0,,The time for judgment has come, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:56.23,Main,,0,0,0,,"Incoming Call: Blocked Number"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:02.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Is your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:06.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.87,0:15:10.03,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a challenge from the Wall of Severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:15.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki,\Nif your love is true, go to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:17.67,Main,,0,0,0,,The bears are waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:22.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Give yourself over to the bears,\Nand your love will be approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:28.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive bears. I'll ruin bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:35.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Kureha Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:38.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurizono? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:40.57,Main,,0,0,0,,To eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:41.69,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:47.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Here's something you'll want to know:\N{\i1}I'm {\i0}the one who ate your beloved Sumika Izumino.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:51.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Me, Mitsuko Yurizono. I'm a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:53.45,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:57.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I suppose you can't believe it, but I'm a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:16:00.71,Main,,0,0,0,,A bear pretending to be human,\Nif we're being precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.63,Main,,0,0,0,,A bear pretending to be human?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:07.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. So was that bear I shot, Konomi Yurikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:10.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikawa? But she was your--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:17.77,Main,,0,0,0,,"Friend"? Maybe so.\NWhile she obeyed me, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:24.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you know? When you're\Ndeciding to be friends with someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,the only important thing is that\Nshe's just a little bit inferior to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.70,Main,,0,0,0,,That way she's easy to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:37.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You look so incredulous! All right, then--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:40.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll show you proof that I'm a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Those are Sumika's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:46.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Believe me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:49.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, she was a freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:54.85,Main,,0,0,0,,She was getting {\i1}eaten{\i0},\Nand all she did was worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:17:04.94,Main,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry, Kureha! I can't fix your love,\Nyour mother's flowerbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:08.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Even though I promised I wouldn't back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:12.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kureha... I'm sorry..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:22.21,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have it in you to shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:27.51,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:32.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Right there, that rage in your eyes--\Nit's so {\i1}good{\i0}... it's getting me off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:34.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Your blood is boiling in your veins!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:39.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}smell{\i0}. You smell like I can hardly stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:41.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, get angrier for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:48.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive bears. I'll ruin bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:53.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you: you don't have it in you to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:56.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Grawr... grawr...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:59.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Gra-ra-rawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:04.67,Main,,0,0,0,,No way! This can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:08.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Tee-hee. Missed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Missed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:14.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Missed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:16.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Grawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:20.06,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all right. In place of the Sumika I ate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.06,0:18:23.89,Main,,0,0,0,,...{\i1}I'll {\i0}love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:37.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to eat her! I want to eat her right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:44.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Court is in session!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:55.59,MainTop,,0,0,0,,We now begin the Yuri Trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:59.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Your Honor, give us yuri approval, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:02.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to save Kureha Tsubaki, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:05.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Save Kureha Tsubaki?\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:07.90,Main,,0,0,0,,You two are {\i1}bears{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:14.86,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll eat humans! If we don't eat them,\Nwe can't protect Ginko's love!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:19.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Ha, so you admit your crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:21.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:26.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Objection! For a bear,\Neating humans is no crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:28.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Sparkle, sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:33.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry, rule! It has to be now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:36.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. That's the sexy way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:40.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Shaba-da-doo. So, defendant-bears...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:45.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you be invisible?\NOr will you eat humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:46.73,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:47.77,Main,,0,0,0,,...humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:52.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I now declare the verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:55.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:20:00.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:07.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:09.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:17.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:21.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Ra-ra-rawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:30.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:43.28,Main,,0,0,0,,You won't back down on your love, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:47.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl. Only love can change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:54.96,Main,,0,0,0,,My... love...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:56.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:58.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:01.47,Main,,0,0,0,,--Mmm.\N--Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:06.97,Main,,0,0,0,,What is this? Their tongues\Nfeel rough, but... warm and kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:09.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I've felt this somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:14.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Smooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:16.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:24.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:27.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Give me the Promise Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:29.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Grawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:34.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Gra-ra-ra! Gra-ra-ra-ra-rawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:42.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I... killed her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:44.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I killed Yurizono?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.68,0:21:47.18,Main,,0,0,0,,No, this can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:50.18,Main,,0,0,0,,A bear in human form... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:51.69,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:07.24,Main,,0,0,0,,What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:11.37,Main,,0,0,0,,If it's the Exclusion Ceremony,\Nyou can't participate yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.37,0:22:15.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Because you can't be our friend until\Nyou take part in the Invisible Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:16.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:22.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! So instead, we'll tell you\Nsomething you'll want to know, Oniyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:23.93,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.93,0:22:28.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, where do you think\Nyour missing friends are?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.22,0:22:31.43,Main,,0,0,0,,"Missing"? You mean like Akae?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:33.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:37.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.07,0:22:40.90,Main,,0,0,0,,This is where we buried the parts\Nof Katyusha Akae we didn't eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:41.65,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Katyusha Akae・(Yuri)"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.65,0:22:44.99,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Muahaha! We're super nice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.99,0:22:50.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you mean, you ate Akae?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.12,0:22:53.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.42,0:22:55.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Grrrr.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.96,0:22:57.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.42,0:22:58.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Because we're about to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.88,0:23:02.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:03.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Bear shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.80,0:23:05.76,Main,,0,0,0,,...eat {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.76,0:23:07.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Slurp.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.70,0:23:31.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the boundary that severed{\i0}\N{\i1}ripe moon from sleeping forest{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.70,0:23:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Break the law God shackles us with and smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.38,0:23:45.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I turned away from the bleating flock{\i0}\N{\i1}of shadows and howled my bloodthirsty ego{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:52.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here amidst the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.02,0:23:55.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Overflowing honey and soul{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.39,0:23:58.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to rend silk with my fangs{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.86,0:24:05.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm afraid you'll vanish{\i0}\N{\i1}like the world's last ray of hope{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.90,0:24:12.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The savage beast inside me{\i0}\N{\i1}tore out the throat of innocence{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.74,0:24:22.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, shoot me through the heart{\i0}\N{\i1}with your sweet-scented Barrett of love{\i0}
